 height=69 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/387739a905bc07ae731e1bd8469001f9.webp?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/55ef34e71e2a97928b35b00f711b3fe1.avif?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=222 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/154c6264ba254fba2d43fa0cb9d4e884.poster.avif?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/154c6264ba254fba2d43fa0cb9d4e884.webm?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/154c6264ba254fba2d43fa0cb9d4e884.mp4?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore through the world as you search for a cure to your froggy-curse! Use magical portals to travel between locations as you navigate around solving problems.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/464c4f88bb88bc9257626999259e9b5c.webp?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=63 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/387739a905bc07ae731e1bd8469001f9.webp?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/68b44453c44fb51086e3fa2451bc09e6.poste