/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/e5612f4d391968ec65008de10be3e752.webm?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/e5612f4d391968ec65008de10be3e752.mp4?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/19ee0a1f259a2fcd9085c32b7db4cba0.poster.avif?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/19ee0a1f259a2fcd9085c32b7db4cba0.webm?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/19ee0a1f259a2fcd9085c32b7db4cba0.mp4?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/81720ba0f86ed0b7d5697051316f2662.poster.avif?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/81720ba0f86ed0b7d5697051316f2662.webm?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/81720ba0f86ed0b7d5697051316f2662.mp4?t=1739070410\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Magic?! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No, Potions! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Throw them to solve puzzles and interact with the world! Scan all sorts of things as you run around, you might find out about a new Potion or some cool frog facts! maybe even a secret society unbeknownst to the general public awaiting for their time to break free and revolutionize Alecost!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3174410/extras/387739a905bc07ae731e1bd8469001f9.webp?t=1739070410\" width=600 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
